ects of these drugs and in whom toxicity symptoms may be easily overlooked.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/158292/', '', 'Imipramine', 'Protriptyline, Viloxazine', 1767369485);
