henelzine, Tranylcypromine, Desvenlafaxine, St. John''s Wort, Isocarboxazid, Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Vortioxetine, Milnacipran, Tryptophan, Levomilnacipran, More', 'Potassium bicarbonate, Potassium gluconate, Calcium chloride, Zinc sulfate, Magnesium sulfate, Sodium acetate, Arginine, Sodium glycerophosphate, Zinc chloride, Sodium bicarbonate, Sodium chloride, More', 1767369485);
